abstract: >-
  Local data preprocessing for AI — structured summaries, governed
  access, auditable answers. Tailor is a local-first MCP framework
  that lets any MCP-speaking AI work with your own data without
  that data ever leaving your machine, with every action recorded
  in a durable audit log and results stamped for reproducibility.
